title: What is the name of this phone? - Quora

response.answer_text: Nokia manufactured the 7610 smartphone, Nokia's first smartphone, featuring a 1 megapixel camera (1152x864 pixels), in mid-2004. It was targeted at the "fashion conscious" individual.Other pre-installed applications include the Opera Mobile web browser and Kodak Photo Sharing. The Nokia 6670 is the same phone with a more conventional keypad layout, and slightly different pre-installed software, aimed at business users.
